By Esther Clark|0
By Esther Clark|0
A star rating of 4.3 out of 5.90 ratingsRate|0
A star rating of 4.3 out of 5.90 ratingsRate|0
Preparation and cooking timePrep:15 minsCook:25 mins|0
Preparation and cooking timePrep:15 minsCook:25 mins|0
Preparation and cooking time|0
Prep:15 minsCook:25 mins|0
Prep:15 mins|0
Cook:25 mins|0
Easy|0
Easy|0
Easy|0
Serves 4|0
Serves 4|0
Serves 4|0
Make this creamy mushroom pasta dish on days when you need a big bowl of comfort. Cream, parmesan, white wine, lemon zest and parsley make this a rich and flavourful dinner|0
Make this creamy mushroom pasta dish on days when you need a big bowl of comfort. Cream, parmesan, white wine, lemon zest and parsley make this a rich and flavourful dinner|0
Make this creamy mushroom pasta dish on days when you need a big bowl of comfort. Cream, parmesan, white wine, lemon zest and parsley make this a rich and flavourful dinner|0
